{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "拔銃相助", "storyInfo": "為了答謝陳，水月將自己的金塊送給了陳。\n而後，陳與林雨霞繼續搜索線索無果，最終順利晉級。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太驚人了，陳女俠，先是殺入巷子中救下被圍攻的水月選手，然後直接在巷子中與其他參賽選手對峙。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他隊伍看來也已經認定鼠膽龍威隊是個巨大的威脅，非常默契地達成了聯手。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是即使如此，陳女俠也絲毫不懼，選擇與他們開戰。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是一場酣暢淋漓的戰鬥！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我們也不能忘記在巷子的另一邊，林女俠的戰鬥！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和陳女俠在巷子中激烈的戰鬥不同，林女俠在巷子口僅憑幾招就威懾住了趕來的其他隊伍。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次大獎賽中，真的有能夠戰勝這個組合的隊伍存在嗎？！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，這兩個人果然還是適合各打各的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，Missy，你猜老陳和林小姐對打的話，誰會贏？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問這個幹嘛？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是很感興趣啊，兩個很厲害的人放一起，一般都會想知道誰更厲害吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有你才會這麼想吧！", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正我不知道，今天是我這幾年第一次看到這個女人真的出手。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？你不是和林小姐關係很好嗎，這都沒見過。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰和她關係好啊，整天神神秘秘的，有的時候電話都打不通。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且誰說熟了就一定要看過對方動手啊。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有道理，看來是我跟老陳相處習慣了。老陳現在想贏我可不能只靠她那套劍法了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把所有人都當成你們倆好不好。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，我沒見過才好，我怕哪天我見到的時候就是要抓她的時候了。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有道理，畢竟是那位鼠王的女兒。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，不過也不能這麼說，那位也不是什麼壞人。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛來龍門混的時候......", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，我又不是沒見過鼠王，還用你告訴我。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，你明白就好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起這個，你剛才用了“混”字吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧我，在詩大小姐面前說粗話，該掌嘴。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你和老陳就見過她出手啊？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這不是沒有才來問你嘛，老陳我估計也沒有。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一點你說得倒是沒錯，沒見過她出手對我們這種立場的人是好事，不然熟歸熟，該做的少不了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道就好。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我也沒想到，居然會有老陳和她聯手的一天。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是活久了什麼都能見到。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說回剛才的話題，所以你覺得誰會贏？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懶得猜。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，那我自己猜。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，老陳要是拿著劍，林雨霞大概很難近她的身。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，要是讓林雨霞近了身，老陳就輸定了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳這麼菜。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不能這麼說，老陳的拳腳功夫肯定是不差的，擒拿、關節技什麼的，我們平時培訓的她都做得很好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看她剛才打的，她用銃準頭也不差。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是老陳畢竟拿手的是劍術。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是林雨霞的拳腳功夫相當於老陳的劍術。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳暉潔，逞英雄開心嗎？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怎麼開心，不過也不用你操心。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，陳小姐，我......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說了，你在那裡等我就好，你做得沒有問題。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你幫了我。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客氣。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你為什麼要幫我呢？", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不為什麼，看到了，就幫了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣啊。姐姐你是個好人呢。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這樣，給。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......赤金？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我剛才就是想拿這個才被他們圍住的。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我們沒關係嗎？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我再去找就是了。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我本來就不是很在乎比賽，能夠認識陳姐姐這樣的好人，對我來說已經很滿足了。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提醒一下，這裡已經驚動了不少隊伍，想聊天可以，別在這裡停留太久比較好。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就先走啦，拜拜~", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也走吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姑且問一下，你那邊除了逞英雄還有什麼收獲嗎？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤金不算收獲？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也行。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒什麼特別的。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，繼續？還是交了？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先繼續吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, 